uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.forms.inputs

Class OptionalListInputWrapper<V,T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.forms.inputs.OptionalListInputWrapper<V,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - value type
    T - item type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Input<V>, ItemInput<T>, ListInput<V,T>, OptionalInput, OptionalListInput<V,T>

    public class OptionalListInputWrapper<V,T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements OptionalListInput<V,T>
    Adapter to convert a ListInput into a OptionalListInput returning null on not selected. This also allows the un-selected text to be customised.
    Author:
    spb
